## 7. Working Principle

1. Environmental data is collected through connected sensors.
2. ESP32 reads and processes the sensor values.
3. The processed data is transmitted to the Blynk cloud through Wi-Fi.
4. Blynk updates the mobile dashboard in real time.
5. Users can remotely monitor temperature, humidity, gas level, soil moisture, and water level.

